* Pete Cortese – rhythm guitar 
* Tom Gomes – drums 
* Howard Jones – lead vocals 

Live
* Patrick Lachman – guitar, backing vocals 
* Philip Labonte – lead vocals 
* Jordan Mancino – drums 
* Josh Mihlek – guitar 
